445
00:27:10,044 --> 00:27:11,128
ingatanmu akan dihapus.

446
00:27:11,879 --> 00:27:13,672
Tim Intervensi akan menghapus ingatanmu.

447
00:27:14,673 --> 00:27:19,011
Emosimu, kenanganmu,
seluruh kepribadianmu akan dihilangkan.

448
00:27:19,887 --> 00:27:21,764
Teman dan keluargamu
akan mengira kau gila.

449
00:27:22,723 --> 00:27:25,434
Kau tak akan memikirkan apa pun.

450
00:27:31,523 --> 00:27:32,524
Kau paham?

451
