460
00:28:00,886 --> 00:28:02,721
Ada apa dengan kalian? Astaga!

461
00:28:06,475 --> 00:28:08,602
Ayolah. Jangan!

462
00:28:09,770 --> 00:28:10,979
Apa-apaan ini?

463
00:28:12,731 --> 00:28:13,732
Benarkah?

464
00:28:15,651 --> 00:28:16,652
Apa-apaan ini?

465
00:28:18,695 --> 00:28:19,696
Baiklah.

